\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΛΕ̄\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"xly-Latn\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020131_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020131_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020131.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020131-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Agostiniani 1977 (IAS I)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Λεω, Alessio 1970\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Λεω or Λεο-, Lejeune 1970\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Abbreviation ΛΕ frequently used on Attic vases with the value of λήκυθος. However, there are no examples of this abbreviation associated with a value notation. Agostianiani suggests interpreting the alphabetical sign as a value notation (one obol), thus proposing to translate how: \"One lekythos (corresponding to the value of) one obol\". See also Hackl 1909, p.98.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Tusa 1960 no.12 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001542\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001542\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Schmoll 1961 68 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001602\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001602\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Alessio 1970 60 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002566\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002566\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Lejeune 1970 148, 161, 163 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001880\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001880\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Agostiniani 1977 131 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002201\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002201\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Hackl 1909 98 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002565\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002565\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1  5-6  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[259,262,265,268,271,273,276,279,282],{"id":260,"html":261},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"xly-Grek\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>val03 (uncertain interpretation) \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>λε̄́(κυθος) \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \